                      Section 1 - Software Setup and Troubleshooting
1 - Installing Java,Eclipse and Tomcat
This section covers the installation the necessary software for the course
Java - SDK needed available at - http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
Eclipse - IDE available at - https://eclipse.org/downloads/
Tomcat - Webserver available at - http://tomcat.apache.org
  **** Different platforms will have different requirements 
 
